| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7488 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2b2cb977-e18c-5ec7-8f77-f5d6a696bdea"
